"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 445px; height: 427px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Ossification of the anterior longitudinal ligament, similar in appearance to flowing candle wax (arrow), is seen in the lateral view of the thoracic spine (left radiograph) in a patient with diffuse idiopathic skeletal hyperostosis (DISH). The changes are predominantly on the right side, particularly in mid-thoracic spine (anteroposterior view, right radiograph). There is both complete and incomplete bridging of the spurs.",
